item.title: Animal Creation Tutorial
item.description: Animal Creation Tutorial Hi future designer! I’m Belgian Shepard also knowed as Octavio17493 and ill teach u how to code with this tutorial, hope you can make your animals with my help, so lets go with basic things first. 1 – Basic things Ok, before coding ill say u what do u need: Choose a codename for your animal. This codename mustn’t have spaces, -, ? or rare characters, only letters.
